---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Contact | Dining Unhinged">

<section class="contact-page">

  <h1>Contact</h1>

  <p class="contact-intro">
    Have a restaurant recommendation, cocktail suggestion, collaboration opportunity, or just want to say hello? I'd love to hear from you.
  </p>

  <div class="contact-card">

    <h2>Email</h2>

    <p>
      For restaurant recommendations, media inquiries, partnerships, or general questions, you can reach me at:
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="mailto:diningunhinged@gmail.com">
        diningunhinged@gmail.com
      </a>
    </p>

  </div>

  <div class="contact-card">

    <h2>Restaurant Recommendations</h2>

    <p>
      Know a venue that deserves to be featured? Whether it's a hidden gem, an outstanding cocktail bar, a neighborhood bakery, or a restaurant worth the drive, I'm always looking for my next great meal.
    </p>

  </div>

  <div class="contact-card">

    <h2>Media & Collaborations</h2>

    <p>
      Dining Unhinged is always open to discussing collaborations, media opportunities, and partnerships that align with the publication's values of honest storytelling and genuine dining experiences.
    </p>

  </div>

</section>

</MainLayout>